<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ดูคะแนนสอบวัดความรู้พื้นฐานโรงเรียนอรพิมพ์วิทยา</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sarabun:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Serif+Thai:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        :root {
            --navy: #0f1f3d;
            --navy-light: #1a3260;
            --gold: #c9a84c;
            --gold-light: #e8c96a;
            --gold-pale: #f5e6b8;
            --cream: #faf7f0;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --text-dark: #1a1a2e;
            --text-mid: #4a5568;
            --border: rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.3);
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Sarabun', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--navy);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Decorative background */
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background:
                radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 20% 10%, rgba(201,168,76,0.08) 0%, transparent 60%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 80% at 80% 90%, rgba(26,50,96,0.6) 0%, transparent 60%),
                linear-gradient(160deg, #0a1628 0%, #0f1f3d 50%, #07121e 100%);
            z-index: 0;
        }

        /* Grid pattern overlay */
        body::after {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background-image:
                linear-gradient(rgba(201,168,76,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(201,168,76,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 48px 48px;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .page-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 480px;
        }

        /* School emblem area */
        .emblem {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            animation: fadeDown 0.7s ease both;
        }

        .emblem-icon {
            width: 72px;
            height: 72px;
            margin: 0 auto 1rem;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--gold), var(--gold-light));
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(201,168,76,0.15), 0 0 40px rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
        }

        .emblem-icon svg {
            width: 38px;
            height: 38px;
            fill: var(--navy);
        }

        .school-name {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif Thai', serif;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--gold-light);
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
        }

        /* Card */
        .card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 2.5rem 2.5rem 2rem;
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            box-shadow:
                0 24px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.4),
                inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
            animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.1s ease both;
        }

        .card-header {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .card-title {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif Thai', serif;
            font-size: 1.45rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--white);
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .card-title span {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-family: 'Sarabun', sans-serif;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
            margin-top: 0.3rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .divider {
            width: 48px;
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold), transparent);
            margin: 1rem auto 0;
        }

        /* Form */
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--gold-light);
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        input[type="text"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.85rem 1.1rem;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.25);
            border-radius: 10px;
            color: var(--white);
            font-family: 'Sarabun', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 400;
            transition: all 0.25s ease;
            outline: none;
            -webkit-appearance: none;
        }

        input[type="text"]::placeholder {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        input[type="text"]:focus {
            border-color: var(--gold);
            background: rgba(201,168,76,0.06);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(201,168,76,0.12), 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        input[type="text"]:hover:not(:focus) {
            border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.45);
        }

        /* Submit button */
        .btn-submit {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.95rem 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold) 0%, var(--gold-light) 50%, var(--gold) 100%);
            background-size: 200% 100%;
            background-position: 0% 0%;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            color: var(--navy);
            font-family: 'Sarabun', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(201,168,76,0.25);
        }

        .btn-submit:hover {
            background-position: 100% 0%;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 28px rgba(201,168,76,0.4);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        .btn-submit:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(201,168,76,0.25);
        }

        /* Error message */
        .error-msg {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.6rem;
            margin-top: 1.2rem;
            padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
            background: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.3);
            border-radius: 8px;
            color: #ff8a8a;
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            animation: shake 0.4s ease;
        }

        .error-msg::before {
            content: '⚠';
            font-size: 1rem;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        /* Footer note */
        .footer-note {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 1.8rem;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            letter-spacing: 0.03em;
            animation: fadeUp 0.7s 0.3s ease both;
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeDown {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); }
            to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        @keyframes fadeUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        @keyframes shake {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateX(0); }
            20%       { transform: translateX(-6px); }
            40%       { transform: translateX(6px); }
            60%       { transform: translateX(-4px); }
            80%       { transform: translateX(4px); }
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 520px) {
            .card { padding: 2rem 1.5rem 1.75rem; }
            .card-title { font-size: 1.25rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="page-wrapper">

    <div class="emblem">
        <div class="emblem-icon">
            <!-- School / Academic icon -->
           <img width="100px" height="100px" src="/img/iconop.png" alt="">
        </div>
        <div class="school-name">โรงเรียนอรพิมพ์วิทยา</div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-title">
                ตรวจสอบคะแนนสอบ
                <span>Examination Score Portal</span>
            </div>
            <div class="divider"></div>
        </div>

        <form action="/check-score" method="POST">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="score_id">รหัสผู้สมัคร (ID)</label>
                <input
                    type="text"
                    id="score_id"
                    name="score_id"
                    placeholder="กรอกรหัสผู้สมัคร"
                    oninput="this.value = this.value.replace(/[^0-9]/g, '')"
                    required
                >
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="score_pin">เลขประจำตัวประชาชน</label>
                <input
                    type="text"
                    id="score_pin"
                    name="score_pin"
                    inputmode="numeric"
                    maxlength="13"
                    pattern="\d{13}"
                    placeholder="X-XXXX-XXXXX-XX-X"
                    autocomplete="off"
                    autocorrect="off"
                    spellcheck="false"
                    oninput="this.value = this.value.replace(/[^0-9]/g, '')"
                    required
                >
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">ตรวจสอบข้อมูล</button>
        </form>

        <!-- EJS error block — kept as-is for server-side template -->
        <% if (typeof error !== 'undefined') { %>
            <div class="error-msg"><%= error %></div>
        <% } %>

        <% if (locals.error) { %>
            <div class="error-msg"><%= error %></div>
        <% } %>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-note">ระบบวัดความรู้พื้นฐาน &nbsp;·&nbsp; ปีการศึกษา 2568</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>